<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %> - Trendyol Finans</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
  <style>
    body {
      display: flex;
      height: 100vh;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
    }
    .maintenance-card {
      max-width: 500px;
      box-shadow: 0 0.5rem 1rem rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }
    .icon-large {
      font-size: 5rem;
      color: #0d6efd;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="card maintenance-card mx-auto">
      <div class="card-body text-center p-5">
        <div class="mb-4">
          <i class="bi bi-tools icon-large"></i>
        </div>
        <h2 class="card-title mb-4">Sistem Bakımda</h2>
        <p class="card-text fs-5 mb-4"><%= message %></p>
        <p class="text-muted mb-4">Trendyol Finans Entegrasyon sistemi bakım çalışmaları nedeniyle geçici olarak hizmet veremiyor. Lütfen kısa bir süre sonra tekrar deneyin.</p>
        
        <div class="mt-4 d-flex justify-content-center gap-2">
          <button onclick="window.location.reload()" class="btn btn-primary">
            <i class="bi bi-arrow-clockwise"></i> Sayfayı Yenile
          </button>
          <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">
            <i class="bi bi-house"></i> Ana Sayfa
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-footer text-muted text-center">
        <small>Teknik destek: <a href="mailto:destek@example.com">destek@example.com</a></small>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>